# No env vars needed in production right now — TLS material lives at fixed
# host paths (/etc/yopass/origin.{crt,key}) provisioned by cloud-init in the
# `nevin-platform-infra` yopass-instance module, and the yopass binary reads
# them via the volume mounts in docker-compose.yml.
#
# Kept as a placeholder so the directory shape mirrors deploy/nevin-sandbox/
# in case future config needs an env-var (e.g. a public URL for OIDC, etc.).
